### Notifications API
@host = http://localhost:3001
@token = REPLACE_WITH_ACCESS_TOKEN

### List my notifications
GET {{host}}/api/notifications?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Unread count (header bell-д ашиглана)
GET {{host}}/api/notifications/unread-count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Read нэг
PATCH {{host}}/api/notifications/clx_test/read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Бүгдийг уншсан болгох
POST {{host}}/api/notifications/mark-all-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Устгах
DELETE {{host}}/api/notifications/clx_test
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
